                <div class="tab3 individual-tab-content-wrapper how-measure">
                    <div class="content-wrapper">
                        <div class="left-content-wrapper">
                            <h3>How to measure</h3>
                            <div class="left-content-item-wrapper">
                                <h5>1. Neck</h5>
                                <p>Measure the circumference around your neck, keeping the measuring tape relatively loose to make sure you can breathe freely.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="left-content-item-wrapper">
                                <h5>2. Sleeve</h5>
                                <p>Bend your arm at 90 degrees, place your hand on your hip. Measure the length from the back of your neck to your shoulder, elbow, and wrist.</p>
                            </div>    
                            <div class="left-content-item-wrapper">
                                <h5>3. Chest/Bust</h5>
                                <p>Lift your arms slightly. Breathe in and measure the circumference around the fullest part of your chest.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="left-content-item-wrapper">
                                <h5>4. Under bust</h5>
                                <p>Lift your arms slightly. Breathe in and measure the circumference right under your bust.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="left-content-item-wrapper">
                                <h5>5. Waist</h5>
                                <p>Breathe in and measure the circumference around your natural waist, keeping the measuring tape relatively tight.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="left-content-item-wrapper">
                                <h5>6. Hip</h5>
                                <p>Stand with your heels joint together. measure the circumference around the fullest part of your hips.</p>
                            </div>
